determined therewith.

787
00:32:03,940 --> 00:32:05,760
When X is equal to A,

788
00:32:06,100 --> 00:32:07,650
Y will be equal to B.

789
00:32:07,740 --> 00:32:09,670
So B is a function of A.

790
00:32:10,100 --> 00:32:11,470
The definitional domain, value
domain, and corresponding rule

791
00:32:11,550 --> 00:32:13,160
are the three main elements of a function.

792
00:32:28,380 --> 00:32:31,320
