863
00:35:53,680 --> 00:35:55,350
You three, just sit over there

864
00:35:55,620 --> 00:35:56,170
for a semester.

865
00:35:56,260 --> 00:35:57,320
You heard me?

866
00:35:57,420 --> 00:35:58,210
Until graduation.

867
00:35:58,300 --> 00:35:59,400
For a semester.

868
00:35:59,650 --> 00:36:00,450
Turn your heads around.

869
00:36:00,530 --> 00:36:01,480
Class begins.

870
00:36:18,660 --> 00:36:19,600
Excuse me.

871
00:36:19,860 --> 00:36:20,740
Come in.

872
00:36:28,100 --> 00:36:28,980
What...

873
00:36:29,940 --> 00:36:32,040
What happened between you and Chen Jun He?

874
00:36:32,770 --> 00:36:34,750
Nothing.

875
00:36:34,970 --> 00:36:35,370
Mr Wu.

876
00:36:35,460 --> 00:36:37,830
Chen Jun He is not right in his mind.

877
00:36:38,460 --> 00:36:40,320
I can't do anything with him.

878
00:36:42,330 --> 00:36:43,280
Well...

879
00:36:43,700 --> 00:36:44,630
Li Qing Tong

880
00:36:44,770 --> 00:36:46,480
I'll be frank about this.

881
00:36:47,340 --> 00:36:48,490
Have you experienced,

882
00:36:48,580 --> 00:36:49,560
for example,

883
00:36:51,250 --> 00:36:52,200
something like

884
00:36:52,890 --> 00:36:54,360
puppy love for him?

885
00:36:54,890 --> 00:36:57,070
Of course not.

886
00:36:57,220 --> 00:36:59,240
How is it possible?

887
00:36:59,930 --> 00:37:02,640
I don't want to talk to him at all.

888
00:37:03,180 --> 00:37:04,060
Fine.

889
00:37:04,940 --> 00:37:05,960
What about Wu Zhi Xun?

890
00:37:07,820 --> 00:37:08,920
No.

891
00:37:10,920 --> 00:37:11,770
OK.

892
00:37:11,860 --> 00:37:13,240
I'll believe you this time.

893
00:37:13,590 --> 00:37:14,470
It's senior year of high school.

894
00:37:15,200 --> 00:37:15,850
You have to bear in mind

895
00:37:15,940 --> 00:37:17,870
what is important and what is not.

896
00:37:17,990 --> 00:37:18,870
Understand?

897
00:37:19,060 --> 00:37:20,680
Keep your mind on your studies.

898
00:37:20,900 --> 00:37:21,810
If you can't get into college,

899
00:37:21,900 --> 00:37:23,150
you will regret it.

900
00:37:23,340 --> 00:37:24,320
You know?

901
00:37:25,420 --> 00:37:26,350
OK, go back.

902
00:37:26,890 --> 00:37:28,230
I'll talk to Chen Jun He

903
00:37:28,890 --> 00:37:30,310
and let him find another place.

904
00:37:30,580 --> 00:37:32,360
Go back to your original
positions with Wu Zhi Xun.

905
00:37:33,290 --> 00:37:33,930
Study hard.

906
00:37:34,020 --> 00:37:35,350
Don't mess with him.

907
00:37:44,260 --> 00:37:45,270
Mr Wu.

908
00:37:46,050 --> 00:37:48,910
Why is Chen Jun He in our class?

909
00:37:49,250 --> 00:37:50,680
Hasn't he already graduated?

910
00:37:50,770 --> 00:37:51,410
He failed the exam

911
00:37:51,500 --> 00:37:52,920
and came back for another year.

912
00:37:53,580 --> 00:37:54,810
I regret calling him back.

913
00:37:54,900 --> 00:37:56,270
He caused me trouble as soon as he came.

914
00:37:58,580 --> 00:37:59,460
I...

915
00:37:59,690 --> 00:38:02,210
I was thinking that you
should just let him sit there.

916
00:38:02,300 --> 00:38:03,310
What do you mean?

917
00:38:03,860 --> 00:38:05,450
If you chase him away now

918
00:38:05,530 --> 00:38:07,480
he would come to make
trouble every now and then.

919
00:38:08,460 --> 00:38:10,730
I'd rather be in the corner

920
00:38:10,810 --> 00:38:11,850
and away from the sight of my classmates.

921
00:38:11,940 --> 00:38:13,690
Just let me study peacefully.

922
00:38:13,770 --> 00:38:15,040
Does he dare?

923
00:38:15,700 --> 00:38:17,120
Don't worry.

924
00:38:17,460 --> 00:38:18,400
If he makes trouble again

925
00:38:18,490 --> 00:38:19,490
he will be expelled immediately

926
00:38:19,580 --> 00:38:20,810
and go back to where he comes from.

927
00:38:20,900 --> 00:38:23,010
If he's expelled because of me

928
00:38:23,100 --> 00:38:25,920
it will all be messed
up when it spreads out.

929
00:38:26,300 --> 00:38:27,490
Mr Wu

930
00:38:27,580 --> 00:38:29,370
I've already had enough grievances.

931
00:38:29,460 --> 00:38:30,210
I beg you

932
00:38:30,290 --> 00:38:31,410
to help me this time.

933
00:38:31,490 --> 00:38:33,400
Don't intensify the conflict anymore.

934
00:38:33,740 --> 00:38:35,960
Let me go to class and study securely.

935
00:38:36,580 --> 00:38:37,650
I

936
00:38:37,740 --> 00:38:39,600
don't want to cause any trouble again.

937
00:38:41,540 --> 00:38:42,420
Fine.

938
00:38:43,140 --> 00:38:44,960
I'll give him the last chance.

939
00:38:45,570 --> 00:38:47,200
You two can sit together for now.

940
00:38:47,380 --> 00:38:48,000
Provided

941
00:38:48,090 --> 00:38:49,320
your studies aren't affected

942
00:38:49,410 --> 00:38:50,680
and no rules are broken.

943
00:38:50,850 --> 00:38:51,690
If he makes trouble again

944
00:38:51,780 --> 00:38:52,950
he will be expelled right away.

945
00:38:54,810 --> 00:38:55,690
Thank you, Mr Wu.

946
00:38:55,780 --> 00:38:56,660
Go ahead.

947
00:39:19,100 --> 00:39:20,640
Do you really want to sit here?

948
00:39:21,210 --> 00:39:22,840
You are now my student.

949
00:39:22,970 --> 00:39:23,690
I'll sit

950
00:39:23,780 --> 00:39:24,920
wherever you sit.

951
00:39:27,610 --> 00:39:28,770
What are you two talking about?

952
00:39:28,860 --> 00:39:30,080
Let me join you.

953
00:39:44,780 --> 00:39:47,270
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

954
00:40:03,000 --> 00:40:04,110
What's the smell?

955
00:40:07,260 --> 00:40:08,480
What are you doing?

956
00:40:09,060 --> 00:40:10,120
Eating instant noodles.

957
00:40:11,380 --> 00:40:13,470
We are having a self-study class now.

958
00:40:14,370 --> 00:40:16,080
Can't I be hungry in the self-study class?

959
00:40:16,620 --> 00:40:17,920
You're being distracting.

960
00:40:19,620 --> 00:40:21,370
How is eating instant noodles distracting?

961
00:40:21,460 --> 00:40:22,710
Why are you so sensitive?

962
00:40:23,170 --> 00:40:24,250
If you don't want to sit here,
just go to the front.

963
00:40:24,340 --> 00:40:25,910
No one's forcing you to sit here.

964
00:40:29,480 --> 00:40:30,360
Come here.

965
00:40:38,060 --> 00:40:39,090
Chen Jun He,

966
00:40:39,180 --> 00:40:40,480
what do you want?
